373
00:24:51,083 --> 00:24:52,625
Seperti nenekku,

374
00:24:52,708 --> 00:24:56,083
dan ratusan wanita di sepanjang sejarah.

375
00:24:57,333 --> 00:24:58,458
Seperti ini!

376
00:25:02,208 --> 00:25:07,166
Selamat datang di pertunjukan kehidupan.

377
00:25:07,250 --> 00:25:10,375
Aku butuh tiga sukarelawan.
